@@TJvArrowButton.AllowAllUp
Summary
  Flags if all buttons in a group can be up (depressed).
Description
  AllowAllUp indicates whether or not buttons in the same group all can have the up or depressed
  state.
  When set to True, all buttons may be in the up state, otherwise at least one button in a group must
  be pressed.
See Also
  TJvArrowButton.Down, TJvArrowButton.GroupIndex

