@@TJvArrowButton
<TITLEIMG TJvArrowButton>
#JVCLInfo
<GROUP JVCL.Buttons.Push>
<FLAG Component>
Summary
  Office style button with arrow. Separated click events for button and arrow.
Description
  The TJvArrowButton control implements a button with a drop down arrow, like the buttons used in
  MicroSoft® Office®. The control has separate click events for the button and the arrow.

